Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.38,0:00:07.38,Signs,,0,0,0,,This video is a special video brought to everyone by Shogakukan.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.35,0:00:13.38,Signs,,0,0,0,,When watching this video, please keep the room bright and sit away from the TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.49,0:00:51.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This luxury train is our pride,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.36,0:00:53.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The Royal Express.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.93,0:00:57.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is your opinion, Your Majesty?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.66,0:00:59.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's very nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.07,0:01:03.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We have actually made a very special reservation for her Majesty...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.14,0:01:10.16,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,No, I wanted to meet the Japanese, at least a little, so I make a requested.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.06,0:01:08.44,Signs,,0,0,0,,SELIZABETH
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.72,0:01:14.48,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Even if you say so, the Japanese government feels...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.90,0:01:15.74,Signs,,0,0,0,,SHINNA JIKAN
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.47,0:01:17.39,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I was even able to meet one famous person.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.59,0:01:23.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, you mean Inspector Nakamori who is responsible for escorting you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.36,0:01:26.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, it was the person I met in my private room a few minutes ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.10,0:01:29.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm talking about Kaitou Kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.73,0:01:30.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.65,0:01:32.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What? You meet Kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.64,0:01:34.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you sure, Your Majesty?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.31,0:01:41.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please stand back. This gentleman is from the Japanese police.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.62,0:01:46.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So what exactly was Kid doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.59,0:01:50.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He came to steal the treasure of our Ingram Empire,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.90,0:02:01.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The largest topaz in Europe - "Crystal Mother".
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.83,0:02:04.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.87,0:02:07.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So the note that we received was real...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.51,0:02:11.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But why did he not manage to take the jewel?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.31,0:02:16.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,One glance was enough for him to understand...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.18,0:02:17.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.92,0:02:20.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What? It's fake!?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.39,0:02:22.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.79,0:02:26.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The real one is well hidden elsewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.26,0:02:28.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, Your Majesty, where is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.39,0:02:32.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't tell it even to the inspector.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.20,0:02:37.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After all, Kid might can overhear us now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.31,0:02:42.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Alright! Kid is on this train!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.21,0:02:47.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Search every suspicious person! Search all passengers from head to tail of the train!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.68,0:02:47.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Understood!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.68,0:02:56.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stop it. I can't forgive the disturbing the passengers for the sake of the Ingram Empire.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.59,0:02:58.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, Your Majesty...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.69,0:03:02.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There are still two and a half hours before we reach Osaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.50,0:03:06.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He may try to steal the jewel as he wrote in the note...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.77,0:03:11.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I will protect it, and I'm willing to risking the name of my country for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.44,0:03:14.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your Majesty, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.91,0:03:14.97,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.71,0:03:16.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Phillip?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.01,0:03:18.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That necklace...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.58,0:03:25.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Be quiet. Anyway, didn't I tell you not to leave the room?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.02,0:03:30.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And how many times have I told you to call me in public as "Your Majesty"?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.09,0:03:32.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who is that boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.11,0:03:38.63,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Prince Phillip, son of the late Ingram's ruler, Henry and Her Majesty, Selizabeth.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.71,0:03:38.55,Signs,,0,0,0,,PHILLIP
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.76,0:03:41.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He is the heir to the throne of Ingram Empire.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.80,0:03:46.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. But that jewel looked different before...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.37,0:03:47.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.91,0:03:52.41,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}This is a bug.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.74,0:03:56.55,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}He probably installed it when he went into Her Majesty's room.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.32,0:03:59.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey! Can you hear me, Kaitou Kid!?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.82,0:04:02.60,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}As long as I'm here, you and your finger...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.60,0:04:03.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...won't touch this jewel!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.02,0:04:06.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Remember that! Take that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.06,0:04:10.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is wrong with you all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.60,0:04:15.17,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Your father just yelled at me, damn inspector.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.83,0:04:17.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.44,0:04:21.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why are you so gloomy? Weren't you the one that wanted to ride this train?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.97,0:04:24.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why I asked my dad to get tickets.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.48,0:04:28.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, yes, I'm always grateful to your father.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.55,0:04:33.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Jeez, pull yourself together. We will meet Her Majesty soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.79,0:04:35.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's probably in the saloon now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.05,0:04:39.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So I just booked an appointment, so I can go up to her and say:
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.06,0:04:43.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"I'm the daughter of Inspector Nakamori, who always gets beat by Kid!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.90,0:04:46.16,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.84,0:04:54.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yay! How lucky we are!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.41,0:04:58.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We are on the same train with Her Majesty!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.64,0:05:03.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We will have to thank Kazuha{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r} and the other for inviting us to Osaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.72,0:05:04.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Exactly!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.52,0:05:06.25,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}However...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.86,0:05:13.99,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Why is Inspector Nakamori escorting her?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.03,0:05:19.10,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Did Kaitou Kid send his next warning note?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.86,0:05:24.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you want to go to the saloon car? We might able to meet Her Majesty.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.97,0:05:27.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course, let's go. I want to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.54,0:05:30.34,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Perhaps we will meet Kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.28,0:05:35.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, but all tables in the saloon car have been booked for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.08,0:05:38.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We have many visitors today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.38,0:05:41.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that so? Jeez...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.95,0:05:42.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I really sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.00,0:05:53.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's too bad. Right, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.97,0:05:56.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah. But we will definitely see her when we arrive in Osaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.47,0:06:04.91,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}But I can't sit here and wait. I need to find out whether Kid sent a note or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.58,0:06:24.42,Signs,,0,0,0,,ROSE
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.80,0:06:32.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn, because of this Kid and his unnecessary warnings, the train is full of cops.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.28,0:06:37.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In such a situation, it will not be easy to get that jewel.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.95,0:06:40.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then wouldn't it be easier to take it from Kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.22,0:06:43.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Together with his life.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.96,0:06:51.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We will do so. Kid got in our way too many times.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.49,0:06:55.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And I'll take her Majesty's life.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.43,0:07:01.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A great opportunity to become a famous killer in an instant.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.27,0:07:07.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your Majesty, isn't it about time to tell me where you hide the jewel?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.21,0:07:11.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If I don't know its whereabout, I won't be able to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.65,0:07:16.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you are so worried, then please stay by my side and protect me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.39,0:07:18.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's drink?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.49,0:07:23.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, but I'm on duty...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.36,0:07:28.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, you are the first person to refuse my offer, Inspector.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.93,0:07:32.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay, I changed my mind, one glass won't hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.05,0:07:44.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.35,0:07:46.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.32,0:07:53.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I knew that Europe has the best wines!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.72,0:07:56.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Once you start, you can't stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.93,0:07:57.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.63,0:08:00.09,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}He is drunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.40,0:08:04.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your Majesty, this is my daughter Aoko and her classmate Kaitou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.67,0:08:05.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.00,0:08:07.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you, Your Majesty!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.50,0:08:13.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,These two said that they wanted to ride the same train with you, so I couldn't stop them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.31,0:08:20.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And Kaitou said that he want to see Her Majesty no matter what, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.75,0:08:21.95,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}That was you...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.27,0:08:23.65,Signs,,0,0,0,,Reserved
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.65,0:08:23.78,Signs,,0,0,0,,Reserved
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.78,0:08:23.91,Signs,,0,0,0,,Reserved
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.91,0:08:24.05,Signs,,0,0,0,,Reserved
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.05,0:08:24.15,Signs,,0,0,0,,Reserved
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.15,0:08:24.28,Signs,,0,0,0,,Reserved
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.62,0:08:31.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aoko, just don't bother the guards!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.89,0:08:32.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.93,0:08:35.66,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}And you call this a guard?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.26,0:08:39.37,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}But at least I ended up in Her Majesty's saloon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.97,0:08:42.74,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Now I can search for the place of the jewel as much as I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.14,0:08:45.01,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}What a fortune for Kid{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-sama{\r\be10}.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.51,0:08:49.08,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}But... where could it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.21,0:08:53.91,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I don't think it's in Her Majesty's room, where I checked.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.48,0:08:57.82,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}It turns out that it should be within her reach.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.42,0:08:59.19,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Or...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.30,0:09:09.20,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Cat? Can it be...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.30,0:09:15.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kaitou, are you aware that you've been staring at Her Majesty for a while now?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.10,0:09:18.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You idiot! I was examining the saloon and saw Her Majesty's cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.81,0:09:21.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You mean Caesar? Cute, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.71,0:09:23.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He will soon be two years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.51,0:09:24.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.78,0:09:26.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Phillip Maximilian Ingram.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.18,0:09:28.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me you are...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.62,0:09:29.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The Prince?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.69,0:09:32.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Caesar, come here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.03,0:09:40.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here, this is Caesar.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.60,0:09:41.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You wanted to see him, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.90,0:09:42.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.60,0:09:44.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can I hold him for a second?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.00,0:09:46.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.94,0:09:47.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He ran away under the table!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.00,0:09:49.77,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}This is a chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.81,0:09:52.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What a naughty cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.18,0:09:58.95,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The right eye looks normal. Left eye...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.15,0:10:04.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you alright, Kaitou?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.15,0:10:07.25,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Damn, it's just a normal cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.19,0:10:12.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What a cute toy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.49,0:10:14.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad gave it to me, it's my treasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.83,0:10:17.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, can I see it for a second?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.70,0:10:21.24,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Looks like it's not here either.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.40,0:10:22.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, onii{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.64,0:10:24.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.24,0:10:25.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could it be you are...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.14,0:10:27.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...Kaitou Kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.18,0:10:32.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please don't joke like that! Of course I'm not!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.78,0:10:37.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess I was wrong, even though I know where the jewel is.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.72,0:10:40.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I won't tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.76,0:10:41.96,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}This little brat...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.62,0:10:47.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Prince Phillip, it's not safe here. Please return to your room.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.13,0:10:50.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Her Majesty is unhappy with your behavior.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.67,0:10:51.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.34,0:10:54.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It looks like it's time for you to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.20,0:11:00.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I will not leave! I have to protect mother and the jewel from Kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.41,0:11:02.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You worried about your mother, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.35,0:11:06.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I hate my mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.52,0:11:08.55,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Now, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.16,0:11:22.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She was caring and kind, but she changed after the death of my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.00,0:11:28.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She is angry with me every time she see me, and never listens to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.20,0:11:31.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sure she hates me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.14,0:11:34.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I promised to my father...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.18,0:11:38.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...that I will protect my mother and my country.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.39,0:11:45.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.49,0:11:48.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems like no matter how many times I say it, you still don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.99,0:11:51.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And it's not "mother", but "Her Majesty".
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.79,0:11:53.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your Majesty!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.23,0:11:55.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.30,0:12:01.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I forbid you to come back! Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.74,0:12:03.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your Majesty, you don't have to...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.04,0:12:08.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, leave it. He won't understand until I do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.41,0:12:11.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.45,0:12:13.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.85,0:12:16.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.93,0:12:30.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hello, you're Prince Phillip, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.13,0:12:33.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.90,0:12:37.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Edogawa Conan, a detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.74,0:12:43.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see. As I thought, Kid sent a note.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.75,0:12:47.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're amazing! You're a detective even you're a kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.15,0:12:49.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wonder if you can find the jewel.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.42,0:12:55.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Actually, I don't know where my mother hid it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.16,0:12:57.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you want to hide a leaf, hide it in the forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.13,0:13:06.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now, you can't tell which piece I just moved, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.20,0:13:09.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If there is no forest, you make one yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.74,0:13:12.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Like Gilbert Keith's "The Broken Sword", right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.31,0:13:18.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, these are the words of a famous detective who is considered a rival of Sherlock Holmes, Father Brown.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.61,0:13:24.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In the story, the trick was more violent and frightening, but your mother's tricks are similar to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.39,0:13:28.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, in my opinion, she acted much more insidiously.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.59,0:13:33.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"If you want to hide a leaf - hide it in the forest. If there is no forest - you make one yourself."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.23,0:13:36.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see. So that's why my mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.50,0:13:40.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That was probably after Kid stole it...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.71,0:13:48.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You know so much about Kid, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.38,0:13:51.68,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}This is because we are closely related.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.22,0:13:59.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is it, uncle?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.42,0:14:01.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nothing. Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.76,0:14:11.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How troublesome, I got the wrong room...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.50,0:14:14.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Jeez, Papa, be careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.21,0:14:22.94,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}That man was clearly eavesdropping. Is he Kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.15,0:14:26.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No... I've seen that face somewhere...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.32,0:14:29.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.02,0:14:30.74,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Oh, Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-neechan{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.05,0:14:32.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You went to the toilet and never came back.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.89,0:14:35.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can't just running around like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.37,0:14:48.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We'll be in Osaka in ten minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.20,0:14:52.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems that our genius Kaitou Kid will be left with nothing today.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.51,0:14:55.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This time, the victory is mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.94,0:14:57.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It looks like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.91,0:15:01.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, where is the jewel?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.69,0:15:07.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I will tell you as soon as we arrive in Osaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.22,0:15:10.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Anyway, how about another glass? For victory.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.96,0:15:12.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I already...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.53,0:15:13.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't be that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.10,0:15:15.96,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Damn it. Where is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.37,0:15:18.57,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Where in the world is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.47,0:15:25.11,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Damn, if I don't hurry up, I'll run out of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.08,0:15:30.06,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Where did I see that man?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.03,0:15:32.45,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Damn, I can't remember!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.22,0:15:38.35,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}That's strange... it hasn't changed in awhile...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.15,0:15:40.35,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Usually the shape would...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.09,0:15:42.92,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}That's it! I remembered!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.76,0:15:44.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.96,0:15:50.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry for the wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.33,0:15:51.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.03,0:15:53.87,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}That's it... I understand now...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.10,0:15:55.44,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The hiding place of the jewel.!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.40,0:15:57.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.97,0:16:00.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.58,0:16:02.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, to the toilet...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.61,0:16:03.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Have a save trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.15,0:16:08.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What a cute coaster!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.95,0:16:12.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even the flowers are squeezed out! And it smells good!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.26,0:16:16.42,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Sorry, Aoko.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.99,0:16:19.73,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I can't become Kid in front of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.53,0:16:26.23,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I saw it in the professor's computer!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.85,0:16:31.69,Signs,,0,0,0,,JACKAL
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.44,0:16:28.40,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}His name is Jackal.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.10,0:16:31.34,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The world famous jewel thief.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.01,0:16:34.31,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}And it's also famous for its cruelty...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.51,0:16:41.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The light went out!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.65,0:16:43.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did Kid finally shown up?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.89,0:16:45.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your Majesty!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.32,0:16:52.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't misunderstand! I was only protecting Her Majesty!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.33,0:16:57.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.67,0:17:00.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Which one is your glass?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.70,0:17:01.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.47,0:17:03.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All of you, split up and check one by one.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.91,0:17:09.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you hide the jewel in my glass?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.51,0:17:12.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How risky...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.39,0:17:25.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here it is! I found it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.09,0:17:27.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Crystal Mother is safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.97,0:17:40.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It is a great honor for me to be caught by you again, Your Majesty.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.88,0:17:45.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kaitou Kid? You fool, we're on a train, you have nowhere to run.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.12,0:17:49.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your Majesty, please remember:
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.58,0:17:51.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kaitou Kid is like a ghost in your bedroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.09,0:17:57.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And do not forget that you are not only a queen, but also a mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.57,0:18:04.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stop, Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.94,0:18:08.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.64,0:18:10.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you all doing? After him!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.41,0:18:10.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.28,0:18:15.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's emergency! Let us pass!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.08,0:18:18.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What have I done?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.78,0:18:22.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because of me, the treasure of our country is now lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.95,0:18:25.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Phillip!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.72,0:18:28.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How easy it is to distract you, Inspector.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.36,0:18:31.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Always being fool by my dummy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.99,0:18:33.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're the one who fool, onii{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.70,0:18:36.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Give back the jewel.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.43,0:18:40.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Without it, the people of my country will be in trouble, so give it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.00,0:18:44.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But how did you know that I'm here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.27,0:18:46.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} told me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.61,0:18:50.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan? I see. So he's on this train too?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.45,0:18:56.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And this uncle helped me to climb up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.95,0:18:57.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uncle?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.19,0:19:01.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, he's behind me...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.09,0:19:07.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've been waiting for this, Kaitou Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.57,0:19:11.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.31,0:19:27.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, but I don't have time to play.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.82,0:19:32.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Put down the jewel and look away.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.52,0:19:34.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You don't want this kid killed, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.13,0:19:38.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't, onii{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}, don't give it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.83,0:19:41.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That voice... Phillip!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.73,0:19:44.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh no, it can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.07,0:19:53.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Prince!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.24,0:19:57.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your Majesty!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.78,0:20:02.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't try anything funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.98,0:20:05.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're always interfere me... Come on, turn around!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.72,0:20:09.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The immortal Kaitou Kid...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.82,0:20:11.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...will meet his end here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.73,0:20:13.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, that's how you look at it...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.50,0:20:21.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn you! Don't underestimate me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.79,0:20:41.06,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}He's already taken care of Jackal, then the other one is...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.23,0:20:52.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah-le-le, auntie.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.73,0:20:55.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aren't your socks looks different!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.04,0:20:57.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There used to be white. When did you change them?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.64,0:21:00.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.75,0:21:09.82,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}If you disguise yourself, then do it properly, Lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.15,0:21:15.12,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}As I thought, he got out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.96,0:21:17.09,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}That's mean, Kid...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.16,0:21:18.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.83,0:21:21.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you doing? This is someone else's room!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.66,0:21:22.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-neechan{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.93,0:21:28.77,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Well, it is Kid. He wouldn't get killed that easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.00,0:21:29.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Jeez.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.41,0:21:36.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, are you alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.31,0:21:38.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Give back the jewel!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.35,0:21:42.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What for? And is that what you say to the one who saved your life?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.15,0:21:45.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Without it, the people of my country...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.09,0:21:48.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I won't! I'm not giving it back to a liar.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.56,0:21:48.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.06,0:21:52.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're doing this for your mother, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.76,0:21:56.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You want to return the jewel so that she can praise you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.83,0:21:58.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.80,0:22:00.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Am I right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.07,0:22:10.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then there is a better way to reveal your mother's feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.29,0:22:19.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Phillip, Phillip...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.36,0:22:22.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your Majesty!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.29,0:22:24.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.83,0:22:25.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Phillip!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.36,0:22:33.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, mother, I chased after Kaitou Kid to get the jewel back, but he got away!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.78,0:22:44.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,M-mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.28,0:22:47.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why don't you ever listen to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.22,0:22:50.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why are you always do the dangerous things?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.15,0:22:56.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why then did I become stricter, replacing your father?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.06,0:23:03.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But... But... Thank goodness!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.60,0:23:09.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're okay... thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.11,0:23:13.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.53,0:23:19.58,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}That's great, prince.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.22,0:23:23.48,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Your mother is a genuinely grief stricken Queen of Heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.65,0:23:27.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come on, boy should not cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.66,0:23:30.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And how many times should I tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.93,0:23:33.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Call me "Your Majesty".
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.50,0:23:39.97,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}As I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.00,0:24:26.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.02,0:24:29.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, Kazuha{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r} is waiting for us at the gate!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.79,0:24:31.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then we need to hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.79,0:24:41.93,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}That jewel is real.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.06,0:24:44.93,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}So that Kid didn't manage to steal it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.90,0:24:46.43,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Or is it...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.87,0:24:51.17,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Next time, I'll get to the Jewel of Destiny!
